Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,265)}千尋20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,135)}嘉音20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(75,35)}艾露希不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:28.00,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(65,305)}好過分～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了上次考試得了35分是因為狀態不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的時候也是得過100分的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以來學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  你不信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著  現在就讓媽媽把照片發過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  比起這事  學習…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生的時候得的100分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的時候怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都要教我  是帥哥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是因為喜歡才教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  眼鏡宅和嘉音是熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉音從剛才開始就一直看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為你很噁心才看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯…錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  偶像和眼鏡宅怎麼可能有交集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了快學習
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼剛才開始就盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…請問
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  我們是不是曾經在哪裡見過面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經教了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來自己努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  眼鏡宅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是單獨輔導  結果什麼都沒有教嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  和剛才的那個人  是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能和那種眼鏡宅是朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡宅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡宅是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  說是眼鏡宅  但也沒到眼鏡宅的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.98,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  沒到眼鏡宅的地步吧  那個眼鏡宅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  嘉音才是  和那傢伙認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常會有的  感覺和哪個人見過之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼來著  既視感？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是因為我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但既然是認錯人  還是認錯個好男人的好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  千尋就知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  繼續學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易哥哥大人肯來教我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還在繼續啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補習結束就過來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的學習有進展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哈  老師來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京同學也請教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要回…咦  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:48.72,pos2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)}「幾天後  考試結果」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  100分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木的預測全中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.47,0:20:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  艾麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  艾麗也努力過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是很好的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去錄音室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼努力了  能給我們社團活動室就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞高輕音部？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好嗎  放手去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有全員都得到100分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被你們努力的身姿感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰國武將部？去做吧去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.89,0:21:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  兒玉？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼心情那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神哥哥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶…並沒有消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分  很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習也很在行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉音好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地來給我們看  看來相當高興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  有比100分更讓人高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定  也是對手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的社團活動室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼趕快準備起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊名就決定是那個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.45,0:22:47.99,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(585,342)}{\1c94E8DD}鼓手{\1cBFC270}募集中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是2年B組  所以就叫2B Pencils
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  差不多該開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:22:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are  you  ready？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.15,0:23:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.76,0:24:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待續？
